COVID-19 ON STUDENTS DASHBOARD
Excited to share my Impact of COVID-19 on Students Dashboard created using Microsoft Power BI! 📊
This interactive dashboard provides key insights such as:
🔹 Total Students: 1182
🔹 Avg Online Classes: 3.21
🔹 Total Self Study Time: 3.44K
🔹 Total Sleep Time: 9304
🔹 Total Social Media Time: 2.80K
🔹 Average Age: 20.17
📈 Key Insights from the Dashboard:
• Impact of health issues on students’ fitness during lockdown
• Social media usage analysis (Instagram, YouTube, WhatsApp, etc.)
• Online class experience distribution (Good, Average, Poor)
• Region-wise sleep pattern analysis
• Age-wise self-study trend
• Comparison of sleep and study time based on health conditions
• Interactive filtering by age, online class medium, and stress busters
Through this project, I practiced data cleaning, data modeling, DAX measures, and data visualization using Microsoft Power BI to analyze the impact of COVID-19 on student lifestyle and behavior.
